\'{{wp|bastion}}\'\' or the \'\'{{wp|Bastille}}\'\' and \'\'don\'\' (from δόντι \'\'dónti\'\', Greek for \'\'tooth\'\'; a suffix in various dinosaur names).\n\nTorideps is a combination of 砦 \'\'toride\'\' (fortress) and \'\'{{wp|Triceratops}}\'\'.\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=Rock|type2=Steel\n|ja=トリデプス \'\'Torideps\'\'|jameaning=From {{tt|砦 \'\'toride\'\'|fortress}} and \'\'Triceratops\'\'\n|de=Bollterus|demeaning=From \'\'{{tt|Bollwerk|fortress}}\'\' and \'\'Schilterus\'\' ({{p|Shieldon}})\n|fr=Bastiodon|frmeaning=Same as English name\n|es=Bastiodon|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|it=Bastiodon|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=바리톱스 \'\'Baritops\'\'|komeaning=From 바리아 \'\'barrier\'\' or 바리케이드 \'\'barricade\'\', and 트리케라톱스 \'\'Triceratops\'\'\n|zh_cmn=護城龍 / 护城龙 \'\'Hùchénglóng\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=From {{tt|護 \'\'hù\'\'|to protect}}, {{tt|城 \'\'chéng\'\'|city, castle}}, and {{tt|龍 \'\'lóng\'\'|dragon, a common suffix for dinosaur names}}\n|zh_yue=護城龍 \'\'Wuhsèhnglùhng\'\'|zh_yuemeaning=Same as Mandarin name\n}}\n<br clear="left">\n\n==Related articles==\n* [[Don]]\n\n==External links==\n\n{{-}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Rock|type2=Steel}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Rock|prevnum=410|prev=Shieldon|nextnum=412|next=Burmy}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[Category:Fossil Pokémon]]\n\n[[de:Bollterus]]\n[[es:Bastiodon]]\n[[fr:Bastiodon]]\n[[it:Bastiodon]]\n[[ja:トリデプス]]\n[[zh:护城龙]]'}